# Last War Bot FAQ

## Is there a Last War Bot?

Yes. GnBots provides cloud automation for Last War: Survival.

## Is there a Last War Bot on GitHub?

Most GitHub bots require technical setup.

GnBots runs directly in the cloud without installing code.

## Does it require BlueStacks?

No.

GnBots does not require BlueStacks, Android emulators, or a PC.

## Can it auto join rallies?

Yes.

## Can it scan the map?

Yes.

## Does it run 24/7?

Yes.

GnBots runs from cloud servers.

Start:

https://www.gnbots.com/auto/last-war-bot/
